quran[4{c,v,t}:
9,37,aman ke kis mahinay ko hata kar agay peechay kar dena kufar mein izafah karta hai is se kafir gumraahi mein parre rehtay hain. aik saal to is ko halal samajh letay hain aur dosray saal haraam. taakay adab ke mahino ko jo khuda ne muqarrar kiye hain ginti poori kar len. aur jo khuda ne manakiya hai is ko jaaiz kar len. un ke buray aamaal un ke bhallay dikhayi dete hain. aur khuda kafir logon ko hadaayat nahi diya karta
9,38,momino! tumhekiya howa hai ke jab tum se kaha jata hai ke khuda ki raah mein ( jehaad ke liye ) niklo to tum ( kahili ke sabab se ) zameen par giray jatay ho ( yani gharon se niklana nahi chahtay )kiya tum akhirat ( ki nematon ) ko chore kar dena ki zindagi par khush ho baithy ho. duniya ki zindagi ke faiday to akhirat ke maqabil bohat hi kam hain
9,39,aur agar tum nah niklo ge to khuda tum ko barri takleef ka azaab day ga. aur tumhari jagah aur log peda kar day ga ( jo khuda ke poooray farmanbardar hon ge ) aur tum is ko kuch nuqsaan nah pouncha sakuu ge aur khuda har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
9,40,agar tum paighambar ki madad nah karo ge to khuda unn ka madadgaar hai ( woh waqt tum ko yaad hoga ) jab un ko kafiroon ne ghar se nikaal diya. ( is waqt ) do ( hi aisay shakhs they jin ) mein ( aik abubaker they ) aur dosray ( khud rasool allah ) jab woh dono ghaar ( Sore ) mein they is waqt paighambar apne Rafeeq ko tasalii dete they ke gham nah karo khuda hamaray sath hai. to khuda ne un par taskeen nazil farmai aur un ko aisay lashkaron se madad di jo tum ko nazar nahi atay they aur kafiroon ki baat ko pust kar diya. aur baat to khuda hi ki buland hai. aur khuda zabardast ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
